# Code owners — auto-assign reviewers on every PR.
#
# Syntax: <pattern> <owner>...
# First matching line wins (later patterns override earlier ones).
#
# Today payunivercart is a single-maintainer repo — Kennedy reviews
# everything. When the team grows, split by surface (api/, dashboard/,
# checkout/, workers/, packages/db/, etc.) and assign per-team.

# Default owner — every change defaults to Kennedy until overridden.
*                   @EuKennedy

# Critical infra paths — explicitly Kennedy until a payments/ops team
# exists. These also gate the `Require review from Code Owners` branch
# protection rule.
/.github/           @EuKennedy
/Dockerfile         @EuKennedy
/docker-compose.yml @EuKennedy
/packages/db/       @EuKennedy
/packages/crypto/   @EuKennedy
/packages/audit/    @EuKennedy
/packages/payments/ @EuKennedy
